Package: adRutils
Type: Package
Title: Utility Functions for Data Processing and Statistical Modeling
Version: 1.3.0
Date: 2026-02-03
Authors@R: 
    person("Ana", "Boeriu", , "ana.boeriu@ucsf.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0000-5469-4085"))
Description: A collection of utility functions for data cleaning, transformation, 
    statistical modeling, and file operations. Provides tools for reading and 
    combining CSV files, handling missing values, transforming variables, 
    fitting grouped linear models, and performing pairwise comparisons with 
    flexible p-value formatting. Designed to streamline common data analysis 
    workflows with consistent interfaces and informative feedback.
